HEADWORD: Quadripartite
<hw>Quad*rip"ar*tite</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>quadripartitus</ets>, p. p. of <ets>quadripartire</ets> to divide
into four parts; <ets>quattuor</ets> four + <ets>partire</ets> to
divide: cf. F. <ets>quadripartite</ets>.]</ety> <def>Divided into four
parts.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

